From: Dmitry Eremin-Solenikov <dbaryshkov@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 13 Oct 2016 17:24:11 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] Add GOST R 34.10 curves defined by RFC4357 and newer standard

Signed-off-by: Dmitry Eremin-Solenikov <dbaryshkov@gmail.com>
---
 .gitignore               |   5 ++
 Makefile.in              |  56 ++++++++++--
 ecc-curve.h              |   5 ++
 ecc-gost256cpa.c         | 125 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 ecc-gost256cpb.c         | 143 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 ecc-gost256cpc.c         | 137 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 ecc-gost512a.c           | 125 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 ecc-gost512b.c           | 137 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 ecc-internal.h           |   7 ++
 eccdata.c                | 179 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-----
 examples/ecc-benchmark.c |   5 ++
 testsuite/testutils.c    |  56 +++++++++++-
 12 files changed, 951 insertions(+), 29 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 ecc-gost256cpa.c
 create mode 100644 ecc-gost256cpb.c
 create mode 100644 ecc-gost256cpc.c
 create mode 100644 ecc-gost512a.c
 create mode 100644 ecc-gost512b.c

